b'@0xDEADBEEFCAFE Oops... 8th line should be:\n[ $res != 0 ] && exit $res'

b"@0xDEADBEEFCAFE I use this in .git/hooks/pre-commit:
if [ $(git branch --show-current) == 'master' ]; then
    IFS=$'\n'
    res=0
    for f in $(git diff --name-only --diff-filter=A HEAD); do
        pycodestyle $f
        res=$(($? || $res))
    done
    [ $r != 0 ] && exit $res
fi
exit 0"
